Rapper Folarin Falana aka Falz has stated that he has never been in love. In an interview with his colleague taymesan, the actor said that he has never experienced what it feels like to be in love with the opposite sex. He however said he doesn’t have any problem with women but love has just not found him. “I’ve not been in love before sha. I have never said to a woman in a romantic way that ‘I’m in love with you’. I have never. I have never said ‘I love you to a girl’,” he said.   Cross dresser James Brown returns from UK     Most celebrities reduce their age, Lawani laments     Five Nigerian celebrities with different baby mamas   When asked how he then gets his inspiration from, the rapper alluded it to the fact that an artist has a foundation that comes as a canvas. According to him: “As an artist you have to have canvas, when you have your canvas , you have different colours of paint, you splash anything anywhere.’ ” Recently, I haven’t opened myself up to it. In the beginning, I wasn’t necessarily closing up myself to it but I just didn’t experience it but recently, I closed the door. “I’m just not ready now. I can’t pinpoint anything wrong, I just don’t feel like I’m ready for that serious commitment now that can alter my life.”